    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. Mechanically, the car is functional; the engine starts reliably and it handles city driving well, though it has accumulated high mileage and may require more frequent routine maintenance soon. You will notice some cosmetic issues, including noticeable scratches on the exterior paint and some wear and tear on the interior upholstery. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that performs its primary job well despite its age and visible use.",
