      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy\u2014this car is seriously in showroom condition. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
