    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is derived from the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearings and Double VANOS system have been proactively serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis is reinforced, free of subframe fatigue, and paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black with a factory-fresh Nappa leather interior, this is a turnkey collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
